## ğŸš€ Getting Started

### Installation.
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/Muhuthu/TSP_notebook.git
cd route-optimizer

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt.

# Launch Jupyter
jupyter notebook OptimalRoutePlanner.ipynb

